[background arg="res://Bg/storage_room.png" fade="1.0"]
[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/The_sports_equipment_storage_room.mp3" volume="0.0"]
The sports equipment storage room is dim and dusty. Basketball hoops lean against walls, and volleyball nets hang from hooks.
if {selected_character} == "celestine":
	join Celestine (animated) left
	join Mark (Mark_half) right
	Mark: This place is a mess. Where would someone hide money in here?
	Celestine: Somewhere out of sight. Behind equipment that hasn't been used in a while.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/The_Protagonist_knocks_firmly.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	The Protagonist knocks firmly on the partially open door.
	Celestine: Ryan, we know you're in here. We need to talk.
else:
	join Conrad (half) left
	join Mark (Mark_half) right
	Mark: This place is a mess. Where would someone hide money in here?
	Conrad: Somewhere out of sight. Behind equipment that hasn't been used in a while.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/The_Protagonist_knocks_firmly.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	The Protagonist knocks firmly on the partially open door.
	Conrad: Ryan, we know you're in here. We need to talk.
[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/Silence_Then_the_sound.mp3" volume="0.0"]
Silence. Then the sound of something being set down.
[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/The_door_opens_wider.mp3" volume="0.0"]
The door opens wider. Ryan stands inside, his expression caught between surprise and defiance.
update Mark rightmost
join Ryan (half) right
if {selected_character} == "celestine":
	Ryan: What are you two doing here? This storage is off-limits to non-committee members.
	Celestine: We found something interesting in the computer lab.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/Ryans_jaw_tightens_almost_imperceptibly.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	join Ryan (animated_angry) right
	Ryan's jaw tightens almost imperceptibly.
	Ryan: The computer lab is public. Whatever you found has nothing to do with me.
	Celestine: Really? Then explain this.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/The_Protagonist_holds_up.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	The Protagonist holds up the crumpled budget proposal draft.
	Celestine: Your handwriting. Your margin notes.
	Celestine: "If they won't listen, I'll have to make them see reason."
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/Ryan_waves_his_hand_dismissively.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	Ryan waves his hand dismissively.
	Ryan: So what? I write notes to myself all the time.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/The_Protagonist_pulls_out_the_second_piece.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	The Protagonist pulls out the second piece of paper - the threatening note.
	Celestine: This note was left in Ria's locker three days ago.
	Celestine: "I know what you did with last year's fund. Resign or I'll expose you."
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/Ryans_face_goes_pale.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	audio music "res://assets/audio/bg/chill.mp3" [loop="true"]
	Ryan's face goes pale.
	Celestine: The handwriting is identical, Ryan. Same loops on the 'e'. Same sharp angles on the 'k'.
	Celestine: You wrote this threat. You knew about Ria's mistake because you've been watching the council.
	Celestine: Waiting for your chance.
	Ryan: That... that doesn't prove anything.
	Celestine: The printer logs show you stopped printing for over an hour yesterday evening.
	Celestine: During that exact time, Ms. Santos left the faculty room for coffee.
	Celestine: You saw her leave. You took the key from her unlocked drawer. You opened the council room.
	Celestine: And you took the money.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/Ryan_stands_frozen.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	join Ryan (animated_sad) right
	Ryan stands frozen, his eyes darting around the room.
	Ryan: I...
	Celestine: Where's the money, Ryan?
else:
	Ryan: What are you two doing here? This storage is off-limits to non-committee members.
	Conrad: We found something interesting in the computer lab.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/Ryans_jaw_tightens_almost_imperceptibly.mp3" volume="0.0"]
	join Ryan (animated_angry) right
	Ryan's jaw tightens almost imperceptibly.
	Ryan: The computer lab is public. Whatever you found has nothing to do with me.
	Conrad: Really? Then explain this.
	[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 2/C2S5/The_Protagonist_holds_up.mp3" volume="0.0"]
